        h2a:'How to Rotate an Image Without Uploading',
        steps:['<strong>Select your image</strong> — click "Select Image" or drag and drop any image onto the page.','<strong>Rotate to any angle</strong> — click 90°, 180° or 270° buttons, or drag the handle to rotate to any custom angle. Snaps to 90° increments when close.','<strong>Download your rotated image</strong> — saved instantly to your device.'],
        h2b:"The Best Free Image Rotator That Doesn't Upload Your Files",
        body:'<p>RelahConvert rotates images entirely inside your browser — no upload, no server, no waiting. Rotate to any angle, not just 90° increments. Drag the rotation handle freely or use the preset buttons for quick 90°, 180° and 270° rotation. Supports JPG, PNG, WebP, GIF and BMP.</p>',
