        steps:['<strong>Select your HEIC files</strong> — click "Select Images" or drag and drop iPhone photos onto the page.','<strong>Conversion runs instantly</strong> — entirely inside your browser. No upload, no waiting.','<strong>Download your JPGs</strong> — single file downloads directly; multiple files download as a ZIP.'],
        h2b:"The Best Free HEIC to JPG Converter That Doesn't Upload Your Files",
        body:'<p>HEIC is Apple\'s default iPhone photo format — but it\'s not supported by most apps and websites. Converting HEIC to JPG makes your photos universally compatible. RelahConvert converts HEIC to JPG entirely in your browser with no file upload.</p>',
